objects.name: Vatet, PyXie, Defray777
objects.description: Unit 42 first noticed that there may be a relationship between Vatet, PyXie, and Defray777 when there were remnants and/or detections of all three in various incident response scenarios. After digging deep into each malware family, it became apparent that Vatet, PyXie, and Defray777 are all associated with the same financially motivated threat group that has been operating as early as 2018. Additional details can be viewed on the Unit 42 blog: https://unit42.paloaltonetworks.com/vatet-pyxie-defray777/
